content: कपटः, --टं Fraud, deceit, trick, cheating; कपटशतमयं क्षेत्रमप्रत्ययानां <ls>Pt. 1. 191</ls>; कपटानुसारकुशला <ls>Mk. 9. 5.</ls> --टी A measure equal to the capacity of the hollows of the two hands joined together.
